<item>
<title>四川石棉留守农妇种的黄果柑，为什么杨幂、朱丹都来站台？</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/y3Ce8KJLfB</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/y3Ce8KJLfB</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNLBZt6v5rl71icY7ia6D3uA3MQM1ndmNlCOBNkYMqr7ZUkpavJ8r8LeNQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;900&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.24333333333333335&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNLBZt6v5rl71icY7ia6D3uA3MQM1ndmNlCOBNkYMqr7ZUkpavJ8r8LeNQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lu5r6c0dYJ5VqOaEz76gPN9NciblXAbqI3NhN1QGJhR0sC5YWXLJBLWicIsRUUKOQCwJeIW8AW3sl0bbXySJPzuQ/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;136&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNmvajlBy9qQ9mJ1VZVeOWAs6iagPT2I4bZVI3cibu3Gcfqia29mSqp9cUw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNmvajlBy9qQ9mJ1VZVeOWAs6iagPT2I4bZVI3cibu3Gcfqia29mSqp9cUw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;每年各类柑橘纷纷过季之时，一种神奇的水果就上市了，它就是“石棉黄果柑”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;它由橘、橙天然杂交而成，2月底~4月才成熟，由于品种珍稀，“石棉黄果柑”还受到了农产品地理标志登记保护。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNSQcFYQU7eQ7icwLH0ERj3P20lS89IVmu1FV1B3RvzBqiaOFkKpyVwPog/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNSQcFYQU7eQ7icwLH0ERj3P20lS89IVmu1FV1B3RvzBqiaOFkKpyVwPog/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;黄果柑色泽金黄，果皮像橘皮一般褶皱、易剥离。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNNYnxKMoAfTpIn5U4Q5wq1eJFvQTLBPkBCtBvbqIia9ibkrxLO3TLKKGA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNNYnxKMoAfTpIn5U4Q5wq1eJFvQTLBPkBCtBvbqIia9ibkrxLO3TLKKGA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;果肉又带着橙子的酸甜清香，它的酸甜感非常强烈，丝毫不像催熟的水果那般寡淡。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;又因为晚熟刚上市，一股子新鲜沁人心脾，越吃越上瘾。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNWOdcicBcbFIk14ODJp24RjOGWLAlhCsK4CAv4aFnKMic8wourXGsVHbA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;388&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNWOdcicBcbFIk14ODJp24RjOGWLAlhCsK4CAv4aFnKMic8wourXGsVHbA/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;果汁也很丰富，轻轻一挤，汁水就喷涌而出。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;它曾创下“150分钟售罄10万斤”的众筹预售记录！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;100%&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9ct0mibmINztmpp4bcMF2cUYy0uhwgpmsicscZaE8r8r8DQecuPBwDnMk0zI7lQ9mmBlaPgLRrsiafVw/640?&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.9&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9ct0mibmINztmpp4bcMF2cUYy0uhwgpmsicscZaE8r8r8DQecuPBwDnMk0zI7lQ9mmBlaPgLRrsiafVw/640?&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;1056&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;连杨幂、朱丹等明星都曾在微博上为它站台。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;这颗不简单的石棉黄果柑，来自四川省石棉县，至今已有300多年的种植历史。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;很多人知道它，却是因为两场地震。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNuE5DnFaxibpBHPziayZ6McqNaypw4foMBnO8HwzazR6nicbvgdibFvbwtg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNuE5DnFaxibpBHPziayZ6McqNaypw4foMBnO8HwzazR6nicbvgdibFvbwtg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;石棉县，位于四川贡嘎山下的大渡河中游，全国80%以上的优质黄果柑都产自这里。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;它还是全球25个生物多样性保护地区之一，国宝大熊猫的放归地就在此。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNoTEkQ6XCMkS5XNbiaxaibUTmEic5sDQj1WHm3XyC7DLj0xiaP5fG1XyXRg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNoTEkQ6XCMkS5XNbiaxaibUTmEic5sDQj1WHm3XyC7DLj0xiaP5fG1XyXRg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;在2008年和2013年，这里连续经受了汶川地震、雅安地震两次严重自然灾害。房屋严重毁坏，田地无人打理，一时间安逸的生活被打破了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但石棉人却和黄果柑树一样坚强，很快便重新开始了自己的生活。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNZccFqKc4Vm5DzTA26zpZySLzZ0m6SLESbkUeuJiaia8hzma2axtYiaN1Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNZccFqKc4Vm5DzTA26zpZySLzZ0m6SLESbkUeuJiaia8hzma2axtYiaN1Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;石棉黄果柑的种植、生长周期十分漫长，要经历整整四季，到来年的2月底，果农们才能迎来收获季。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但对于果农来说，比种植更辛苦的，是如何将这些果实悉数卖出，得以补贴家用。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNZibtWsYnQAy89uNk2JwRiafSDq7kQG1LjvHrdhibXxCDhsm8u34nGTlrQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNZibtWsYnQAy89uNk2JwRiafSDq7kQG1LjvHrdhibXxCDhsm8u34nGTlrQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;从石棉县漫山遍野的果实，到包装精美结实的黄果柑礼盒，这中间多亏了“善品公社”的紧密联结。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;作为中国扶贫基金会旗下的社会企业，“善品公社”将当地零散的农户组织起来，形成稳定的供销关系，同果农们一起改善种植技术，提升果实品质。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNibrQwPYCWVZSn4Xia2tylWjw0ZueOAoX60ohbBEWzEZnE5TbEhtVtGRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNibrQwPYCWVZSn4Xia2tylWjw0ZueOAoX60ohbBEWzEZnE5TbEhtVtGRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;种植标准十分规范，并设置了14个关键节点工序技术优化：建园、栽培、修枝、抹芽、疏果、松土、施肥、锄草、灌溉、病虫害防治、采摘、分级、包装、储运。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNpFUicicOfBl7cEeEoPiaPpickJz0ko7Wib4TzH5Zd5KuQ9iaE6Jsps61ibm6w/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNpFUicicOfBl7cEeEoPiaPpickJz0ko7Wib4TzH5Zd5KuQ9iaE6Jsps61ibm6w/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“善品公社”引导果农使用有机肥、生物菌肥等，减少化学肥料的使用，并统一进行采购、发放和技术培训，为果树生长提供最适合的营养条件。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNjg34icy7fgehrqIH7EekhBHibckiaQXibg0WCDW0GAnGUUqsl7YNibqVyFA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNjg34icy7fgehrqIH7EekhBHibckiaQXibg0WCDW0GAnGUUqsl7YNibqVyFA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;定期去林中除草、剪枝、摘坏果，全部都是果农人工一点点养护，这样的果子怎么会不好吃？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;经过科学化管理后，当地的黄果柑无论品质还是收成，都比以前更好了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNwRN5sj2xRiad0B6A5nxC3b9cvGibtHTia1m1spx5ahM4DVpIZNtGVj7EA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7015625&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNwRN5sj2xRiad0B6A5nxC3b9cvGibtHTia1m1spx5ahM4DVpIZNtGVj7EA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;390&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;吃得也安心！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;最新一批果实已于2019年1月24日送检，进行SGS安全认证，共275项农残和重金属均未检出。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNeSAeHrAh5KiceQXPmdKJxsnVbdUMhVSrkgx248mInFja44QtelnqX4w/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNeSAeHrAh5KiceQXPmdKJxsnVbdUMhVSrkgx248mInFja44QtelnqX4w/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;今年新一批的石棉黄果柑已经新鲜上市，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;有30颗装、24颗装两种规格可选。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;两种规格净重相同，仅在果子大小上有细微区别，味道、口感无任何区别，都一样酸甜好吃！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
