&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; 酸甜、多汁、无核的好果子&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNl2Kib3919nSYodEHOaMNuVlnJD2PjTUDLQZBbug3u0GL6IUTKZLzeKw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNl2Kib3919nSYodEHOaMNuVlnJD2PjTUDLQZBbug3u0GL6IUTKZLzeKw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;span&gt;将黄果柑对半切开，你会发现，它作为一颗柑橘，竟然是无核的！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;吃起来更加过瘾，一瓣一瓣直接放嘴里，全是果肉。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;注：黄果柑为杂交品种，会有个别有核的果子，属正常情况，可放心食用。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNoRGVM11SXebBpH0EFyWf9HWtd5ebNKjjHEdsx41MrW4UEsW9QhvIog/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNoRGVM11SXebBpH0EFyWf9HWtd5ebNKjjHEdsx41MrW4UEsW9QhvIog/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;黄果柑酸甜味浓、无核、果肉细腻，用来榨果汁最合适不过。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;而且它的汁水非常丰富，可以不借用任何机器，徒手榨汁。只要对半切开，直接挤压即可。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYN7U0s3cu9k1ibW4JUr2Nu8u4jEpVRSCfmmgAKeGog6SBmIQoeCMXH1fA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYN7U0s3cu9k1ibW4JUr2Nu8u4jEpVRSCfmmgAKeGog6SBmIQoeCMXH1fA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;平时吃的时候也很方便，可以像橘子一样直接剥皮。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYN8JbRic0zbtoR748Q89J4b9QUVDgpZsUnyFGZEzXT0M9QTv4XUqrHJdA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYN8JbRic0zbtoR748Q89J4b9QUVDgpZsUnyFGZEzXT0M9QTv4XUqrHJdA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;果肉细腻化渣，皮肉好分离。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;不喜欢吃果瓣外那层白色膜衣的小伙伴，也可以将它轻松撕掉。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;一口咬下，尽情享受它丰富的汁水和清新的果香。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNK73zKLK0OAyia8BAKr8bvVCpLuMDicbIcal6vb5oZpbBPxDdPApzYXwg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNK73zKLK0OAyia8BAKr8bvVCpLuMDicbIcal6vb5oZpbBPxDdPApzYXwg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;现在这个时节，还能吃到如此新鲜、酸甜感如此强烈、果香如此浓郁的柑橘，实在难得！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;一条生活馆的小伙伴，吃过的全说好，完全是供不应求的状态。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNcrKIGPaRiafUceh70cdRRx4XKYmqTYulrC0jTfWewkXagvVP6fNxwzQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNcrKIGPaRiafUceh70cdRRx4XKYmqTYulrC0jTfWewkXagvVP6fNxwzQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;30颗装，内含两层，每层15颗。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNuMb1HmfGz7A951WsicBZkO1wX8icZChgKUYIhpT3uwjKIQNaQwxL0V5A/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNuMb1HmfGz7A951WsicBZkO1wX8icZChgKUYIhpT3uwjKIQNaQwxL0V5A/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;24颗装，内含两层，每层12颗。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;每一颗黄果柑都用纸板隔开，拥有自己的空间，尽可能避免运输途中的磕碰损伤。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“善品公社”石棉黄果柑，现一条生活馆有售▼&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7sUxh38yDw3V6UbJ5KgDeVr1Bu4ZcJSXvpRCyQ930fYl5Jiaeyedoo4b4d85ticiawpYnnFwr06aHBWr8qbGAs51g/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-w=&quot;900&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.40444444444444444&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7sUxh38yDw3V6UbJ5KgDeVr1Bu4ZcJSXvpRCyQ930fYl5Jiaeyedoo4b4d85ticiawpYnnFwr06aHBWr8qbGAs51g/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-backw=&quot;554&quot; data-backh=&quot;224&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;262&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;554&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;30颗装，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;净重：4.1±0.1kg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;日常销售价：¥65&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;24颗装，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;净重：4.1±0.1kg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;日常销售价：¥69&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;现在购买可享：同款第二件半价&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;特惠截止至3月15日23:59&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;石棉春晖，致敬天下母亲&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNJHu9SviciaTFekdeWdPjJYZt45YTWCWcL0rK2wJZuq9LFSpTKHvW6NibQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNJHu9SviciaTFekdeWdPjJYZt45YTWCWcL0rK2wJZuq9LFSpTKHvW6NibQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;有别于传统的男耕女织生产方式，在石棉当地，果园中的女性劳动者，占了大多数。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNgkfRmMleo2KGTIe27vbqBmDsJBaDMRib0myAx7lo6gMQ30Zzc44ggRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;她们的丈夫、儿子大多都进城务工了，种植耕作这种粗重活，就这样同老人、孩子一起，托付给了当地的女人们。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNTuKwKiaAz6I3SBJSEdaJzRY05cdxVsib70LmYq1KnveicJR4Vx5uwwupA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但这丝毫没有难倒勤劳乐观的她们，照样把果园和家庭料理得有模有样。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“善品公社”与当地300多户果农建立了长期合作关系，帮助共建农户增加经济收益。这些农户中，就有许多可敬的劳动妇女们。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYN9rcyicA7ZnJLuLMdZ4LkQibo0GXLvksNkfh9knSnIpKSMhAOXbvt12AQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;371&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;80多岁高龄的宋文秀奶奶，劳作之余历时一年时间，为“善品公社”创作了《果园赞歌》一曲，感念如今生活美好。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;她鼓励三个女儿自由恋爱，她说人要掌握自己的命运、追求自己的幸福。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNHsegyuTO0WtPc7H3icCm5wlZicyKL3gtlstJARTrcyhFML6riabictaGUQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNHsegyuTO0WtPc7H3icCm5wlZicyKL3gtlstJARTrcyhFML6riabictaGUQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;371&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;彝族妇女刘林心，十几年前举家从冕宁搬至石棉，如今已经可以说一口道地的四川话。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;她说，2亩黄果柑和3个孩子，是一家人最大的财富。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNGu7SibNiaA6Ydu9AwYlt5Bfr1ickOfLVqtb8WpcCj9Oic3eLEg6c2VicIQg/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNGu7SibNiaA6Ydu9AwYlt5Bfr1ickOfLVqtb8WpcCj9Oic3eLEg6c2VicIQg/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“善品公社”在这些种植黄果柑的女性身上，看到了坚忍、宽容和爱。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNUuYoiaLibTDFrfibZPAcMbR3A4icf41gW8fyccMb7ttsvqx2zaIEvDFJGQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lu5r6c0dYJ5otBV8wdNvG1CNv3k7qBYNCCUdXTECg7LuVAjxzTLmRhkERkbbmf5GTZYz5bqTjX3VibIarFet9zA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;417&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;今年新一批的石棉黄果柑已经到了最佳采收期，预计4月中旬就要下市。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;要尝鲜，得趁早。不但能吃到一年只此一季的黄果柑，还能以购买来支持石棉当地果农们恢复产业，给那些辛勤坚韧的妇女、留守的老人儿童更多力量。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7sUxh38yDw3V6UbJ5KgDeVr1Bu4ZcJSX0KXUrcr95R3Q5VrrjkhzlOYg5C6KVcc3PxulWKGQfc11Ex9jEKfpFQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-w=&quot;900&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.0377777777777777&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7sUxh38yDw3V6UbJ5KgDeVr1Bu4ZcJSX0KXUrcr95R3Q5VrrjkhzlOYg5C6KVcc3PxulWKGQfc11Ex9jEKfpFQ/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-backw=&quot;556&quot; data-backh=&quot;577&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;577&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;556&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/7sUxh38yDw3BMoDQiaYEbfB3subtr3OIibQLQwTQAOIVn3JQtX10hYia73dlRPQLWTwdOuznMicRk2UBBG65PfvHcQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;974&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.28542094455852157&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7sUxh38yDw0j6WaA41JAngiawlAOaHwWyDKboPzrJWy3O94mWjQb69lFcFm1H1q8ez79icBH1AASjzul7q8fawnQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-w=&quot;900&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.14222222222222222&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

